OUR STORY
/$
$
For us, family is everything. Pan Asian Cuisine is a small family owned dine-in restaurant that serves the Green Cove Springs community. Since we've opened over a decade ago, we've made it our mission to treat every customer like family. We make sure our food is the highest quality and always put service as our #1 priority.

THE OWNER
/$
$
Hi, my name's Pamela! My husband and I run Pan Asian Cuisine. When you stop by, you'll see me serving customers or managing our workers to ensure the highest quality service. I put love into everything I do and I hope you get the chance to stop by the restaurant!

SUSHI CHEF
/$
$
Hi, my name is Robert and I'm the head sushi chef at Pan Asian Cuisine! I've had decades of experience making sushi with sushi masters all over the world. I've brought my expertise and creativity to Green Cove Springs so that you can experience some of the best sushi in the world.
